metadata.name: OG Gen 1. Right Click Save As BLUE #001
metadata.description:
The first ever NFT drop from Aqua Culture. Wear this shirt with pride at your next aquarium show or keep it as a collectible along with the NFT. 

We will call upon holders of this shirt for exclusive drops, content, giveaways and also future events in later years so don't ever throw it away! 

Only for the real OG's and we know that YOU WERE FIRST!

Only 50 BLUE shirts will ever be printed. Once purchased, you can contact us on any socials you love to use to give us your sizing. Due to minimum print runs, we will only print and deliver this shirt at the end of every month. So if you purchase at the start of the month, please remember you won't receive the item until the second week of the following month.
